@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 120
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

actor "User" as AUser

rectangle "Traffic Camera Browser" {
  boundary "Registration/Login UI" as UI
  control "Registration Controller" as RC
  entity "User" as UserEntity
}

actor "Authentication Service" as AS

AUser --> UI : enter info + submit
UI --> RC : registration request
RC --> UserEntity : create user record
RC --> AS : validate credentials\nhash password
RC --> UI : show success/error

note bottom of UI
Users can find a registration/login
button in the corner of the page.
end note
@enduml